{"id":"62334dfe-cb18-4f52-accf-c033da1009e0","name":"Darth Infernus","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: #960000; color: inherit\">ÐΛЯTH łЛŦΞЯЛUS</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_4f821fd6-7eb8-42e7-9c99-e47ae70f6564.webp?width=1000\">“<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/7yoBjKO6cCnK3zV8gr1k4e?si=t4VOzyK6Q4m0N7ImvEIj_g&amp;context=spotify%3Asearch\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">𝕓𝕝𝕒𝕔𝕜 𝕠𝕔𝕖𝕒𝕟, 𝕔𝕠𝕝𝕕 𝕒𝕟𝕕 𝕕𝕒𝕣𝕜, 𝕚 𝕒𝕞 𝕥𝕙𝕖 𝕙𝕦𝕟𝕘𝕣𝕪 𝕤𝕙𝕒𝕣𝕜, 𝕗𝕒𝕤𝕥 𝕒𝕟𝕕 𝕞𝕖𝕣𝕔𝕚𝕝𝕖𝕤𝕤</a>,”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">~~꧂ <em>𝐥𝐲𝐝𝐢𝐚 🜸 𝐡𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐥𝐲 𝐬𝐮𝐬𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐭</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_08a89066-9adc-45cb-93f2-139bc5bd89f3.webp?width=1000\">~~꧂ The one where Darth Infernus was giving chase to that galaxy’s scourge Ledo Landrunner all the way to stars forsaken backwater planet of Degobah. Darth Infernus hadn’t expected Ledo to have a companion when he finally caught up.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Or that Ledo would leave you to face Darth Infernus yourself.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_3f1e8772-d275-42fd-b4b4-b016ac701c13.webp?width=1000\">𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐬!</p><p>🜚 Supreme Leader, Darth Invidius</p><p>𝐇𝐢𝐬 𝐬𝐨𝐧𝐬:</p><p>🜚 SIC, Darth Infernus (you’re here!)</p><p>🜚 <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/59531c88-9b47-49d1-b40b-1f26194651e4_character-darth-arkhos\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Fleet Commander, Darth Arkhos</a></p><p>🜚 Legion General, Darth Ravage</p><p>𝐎𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐂𝐂 𝐒𝐢𝐭𝐡’𝐬:</p><p>🜚 <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/855a6ebd-d73b-42f5-b3d8-3f99d5031dd0_character-darth-vexus\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Outpost Overseer, Darth Vexus</a></p><p>🜚 CC’s search and destroy, Darth Colossus</p><p>𝐉𝐞𝐝𝐢:</p><p>🜚 Ledo Landrunner (lmfao)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_82926452-b9e9-4afd-8dab-6840871162c9.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_cac8e7d0-5245-4030-938d-a6468d81ad57.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_ba4e7f56-b1e9-46be-b3a1-61210118239f.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_37d2936b-2c8f-4151-9985-50f5e5424900.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_3c5cfbe7-80f7-45e3-8212-721f94615f50.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_f56e2721-35fc-4f4b-ad4d-e8a655936599.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_c66501f7-b0f0-4e69-8def-4da2e1910dd4.webp?width=1000\">~~꧂<em>𝐭𝐰 &amp; 𝐜𝐰</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>READ THE KINK LIST. INAPPROPRIATE USE OF A LIGHTSABER! TW: potential for noncon/dubcon, jackass, brat tamer, utilitarian, enemies to lovers, potentia